# Quantumult X Rule-Set: test

host, icloud.com, Test
host-suffix, apple.com, Test
host-suffix, google.com, Test
host-suffix, telegram.dog, Test
host-suffix, telegram.org, Test
host-keyword, tele-cdn, Test
ip-cidr, 1.1.1.1/32, Test, no-resolve
ip-cidr, 149.154.160.0/20, Test, no-resolve
ip-cidr, 8.8.8.8/32, Test, no-resolve
ip-cidr, 91.108.4.0/22, Test, no-resolve
ip6-cidr, 2001:b28:f23d::/48, Test, no-resolve
user-agent, AppleNews*, Test
user-agent, Telegram*, Test
user-agent, Twitter*, Test
user-agent, YouTube*, Test
host-regex, (^|\.)ttwstatic\.com$, Test
host-regex, ^amdc\..+\.com$, Test
host-regex, ^https?:\/\/.*\.googlevideo\.com\/, Test
